✅ Summary of Paradigms

Feature                    | Java       | Kotlin     | Rust
---------------------------|------------|------------|-------------------------------------
Object-Oriented            | ✅ Yes     | ✅ Yes     | ✅ Yes (via struct + impl)
Functional Programming     | ⚠️ Limited | ✅ Good    | ✅ Strong
Memory Safety              | ⚠️ GC only | ⚠️ GC only | ✅ Ownership + Borrow Checker
Manual Memory Control      | ❌         | ❌         | ✅ Yes
Concurrency (Safe Threads) | ⚠️ Manual  | ⚠️ Manual  | ✅ Built-in safety
Compiles To                | JVM Bytecode | JVM/Native | Native Binary
